-- Foreign investors show appetite for Russia in Moscow Exchange sale-cbank
-- 
-- Wed Jul 02, 2014 03:30AM EDT
-- None



ST PETERSBURG, Russia, July 2 (Reuters) - Around 40 percent of the investors who bought central bank shares in the Moscow exchange <MOEX.MM> came from Russia, 33 pct from Europe, 15 pct from Asia and 10 pct from the United States, a bank official said on Wednesday.

